    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_388066242" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/388066242" />
    <a title="Dean Lisle" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/11721927-dean-lisle"><img alt="Dean Lisle" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1344565448p2/11721927.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/388066242?book_show_action=true">Aug 09, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Dean Lisle" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Dean Lisle" href="/user/show/11721927-dean-lisle">Dean Lisle</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer388066242" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6416781407241671154">Most concise and precise discussion of our broken political system I have read. Cuts unequivocally to the quick, and on top of that, written by a Republican insider! Exceptional indeed. An absolute &quot;must read&quot; for anyone who imagines himself or herself to be an informed voter.</span>
  <span id="freeText6416781407241671154" style="display:none">Most concise and precise discussion of our broken political system I have read. Cuts unequivocally to the quick, and on top of that, written by a Republican insider! Exceptional indeed. An absolute "must read" for anyone who imagines himself or herself to be an informed voter.</span>
  <a data-text-id="6416781407241671154" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


